base 1.6.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
io.spine.annotation
This package contains common annotation types for Java code and generated classes for annotations of Proto types.
io.spine.base
This package provides base data classes for commands, events, errors, rejections, and utilities for working with them.
io.spine.code
This package contains language-neutral classes and interfaces for Spine tools.
io.spine.code.java
This package provides classes for generating and parsing Java code.
io.spine.code.proto
This package provides classes for working with Protobuf code.
io.spine.io
Utility classes for I/O operations.
io.spine.json
This package provides utility classes for working with JSON.
io.spine.logging
This package provides utilities for logging based on SLF4J.
io.spine.net
This package contains classes and interfaces for Internet data types.
io.spine.net.string
This package provides stringifiers for network-related types.
io.spine.option  
io.spine.people  
io.spine.protobuf
This package provides utility classes for working with Google Protobuf implementation in Java.
io.spine.reflect
This package provides utilities for working with Java Reflection.
io.spine.security
This package provides classes for controlling Java code execution security.
io.spine.string
This package provides classes and interfaces related to conversion of objects into a string form and back.
io.spine.tools.protoc.method
This package provides method generation extension point for the Protoc plugins.
io.spine.tools.protoc.nested
This package provides nested class generation extension point for the Protoc plugins.
io.spine.type
This package provides basic types for value objects used in the framework.
io.spine.ui  
io.spine.util
This package contains utilities that can be used by the client code, server code, and business model compiler.
io.spine.validate
This package provides validation classes and interfaces.
io.spine.validate.diags
Provides classes for explaining found violations of validation constraints.
io.spine.validate.option
This package contains the options and the option factories used for message validation.
io.spine.value
Base classes for value objects.
